WEBVTT

00:48.757 --> 00:51.634
EPISODE 9

01:30.131 --> 01:31.257
Dad.

01:32.801 --> 01:34.302
I'm actually...

01:49.734 --> 01:50.777
Dad...

01:54.781 --> 01:55.907
I'm...

02:19.264 --> 02:20.431
Where's Jun-hui?

02:23.977 --> 02:25.019
What?

02:29.899 --> 02:30.859
You silly goose.

02:31.276 --> 02:32.861
Why do you find it

02:33.361 --> 02:35.780
so hard to tell me? You're so silly.

02:37.365 --> 02:39.117
Dad, you knew?

02:41.995 --> 02:43.830
You knew about it?

02:55.341 --> 02:56.926
I thought you were all grown up.

03:04.517 --> 03:05.518
Are you okay?

03:07.896 --> 03:09.188
I'm so worried.

03:13.318 --> 03:14.402
Shall I come over?

03:17.989 --> 03:19.407
You're not crying, are you?

04:53.209 --> 04:54.252
What?

04:55.461 --> 04:56.546
Where are you, Gyeong-seon?

04:57.088 --> 04:57.964
Home.

04:58.589 --> 04:59.924
Are you going to stay home today?

05:00.425 --> 05:01.926
I am not. Why?

05:04.012 --> 05:05.596
I'm at the office.

05:05.930 --> 05:09.100
I didn't tell you before I left,
so I thought you might think I'm home.

05:12.270 --> 05:13.229
Hello?

05:13.646 --> 05:15.648
I won't go to your place, okay?

05:18.192 --> 05:19.527
Why are you talking like that?

05:20.278 --> 05:21.404
Hang up. I have to go.

05:23.197 --> 05:24.198
Okay.

05:51.976 --> 05:54.395
Remember the day you came home upset
and went out after?

05:54.687 --> 05:56.397
I went to your place to steal more beer.

05:57.273 --> 05:59.442
Someone was at the door, so I went out.
It was Jin-a.

06:01.986 --> 06:03.029
She came to my place?

06:03.154 --> 06:05.323
She couldn't find me.
She figured I was with you.

06:06.115 --> 06:07.241
Make a right.

06:07.658 --> 06:08.993
Oh, right...

06:12.497 --> 06:13.664
Where's your head at?

06:22.006 --> 06:23.341
Something's wrong, isn't it?

06:25.551 --> 06:28.137
What is it? Is it something
regarding work?

06:29.180 --> 06:30.264
Or your friend?

06:33.434 --> 06:34.435
It's nothing.

06:36.145 --> 06:37.438
You can't fool me.

06:39.941 --> 06:40.942
What is it?

06:43.194 --> 06:45.696
- What is it?
- I said it's nothing.

06:47.323 --> 06:49.367
Oh, right.
Were you outside of Seoul recently?

06:50.243 --> 06:51.702
I found a receipt in the car.

06:52.370 --> 06:54.580
It was from Myeoncheon,
the place on the way to Dangjin.

06:56.457 --> 06:59.335
But the date on it was the same day
as when Jin-a was there for work.

07:02.505 --> 07:03.714
I drove her there.

07:05.007 --> 07:06.759
You did? Why?

07:07.593 --> 07:11.097
I was struggling to come up with ideas,
so I wanted to get away for a day,

07:11.305 --> 07:12.640
and I heard she was going there.

07:13.474 --> 07:15.601
But why didn't you tell me?
Jin-a didn't tell me either.

07:16.352 --> 07:17.437
It was nothing important.

07:19.856 --> 07:21.190
I'm not kidding.

07:21.274 --> 07:23.067
There's a guy I've been keeping an eye on.

07:23.359 --> 07:25.778
One of my customers--

07:26.195 --> 07:28.114
How much do you even know
about your customers?

07:28.614 --> 07:30.450
Why are you trying to set her up
with any guy?

07:31.117 --> 07:33.703
Don't think like that. He's been coming
to my store for a long time.

07:33.786 --> 07:35.455
He also has a nice job.

07:37.039 --> 07:38.291
Is that all that matters?

07:39.125 --> 07:40.168
Then I'd qualify too.

07:41.627 --> 07:42.795
We don't consider you a man.

07:43.045 --> 07:44.088
Then am I a woman?

08:15.745 --> 08:17.121
Where did they go?

08:19.373 --> 08:21.125
My gosh, what's going on in here?

08:21.334 --> 08:24.462
I told him to get out of my room,
but he wouldn't listen.

08:24.545 --> 08:26.839
- Gosh, please listen to her.
- Seriously.

08:27.131 --> 08:28.466
- When will you grow up?
- Exactly.

08:29.550 --> 08:31.260
I'm hungry. Let's go eat.

08:34.847 --> 08:36.182
Is someone chasing you?

08:36.682 --> 08:38.267
What are you doing at my place?

08:38.559 --> 08:39.727
Your place?

08:41.812 --> 08:43.064
Your place is my place.

08:44.565 --> 08:46.150
I'm tired. Please leave.

08:46.234 --> 08:48.402
Let me finish my beer. Let go of me.

08:50.279 --> 08:51.781
Just take that home.

08:54.075 --> 08:56.160
Take this one too.
Drink up and sleep tight.

08:56.577 --> 08:58.663
No, I'm just going to finish this.

09:00.164 --> 09:01.082
Go on.

09:01.165 --> 09:04.835
Can I please go after I finish this?

09:05.294 --> 09:06.379
Please, my brother?

09:08.297 --> 09:09.465
Okay, fine.

09:09.549 --> 09:12.510
I don't know what you're angry about,
but don't take it out on me.

09:12.593 --> 09:13.803
I'm going to kill you tomorrow.

09:17.181 --> 09:18.182
Why you...

09:54.802 --> 09:55.970
Hello, Ms. Kim.

09:58.014 --> 09:58.973
Pardon?

09:59.640 --> 10:00.725
Where?

10:01.767 --> 10:03.394
Please check him too.

10:03.728 --> 10:05.438
He's like a son to me.

10:06.606 --> 10:07.732
I'm still the eldest son.

10:09.233 --> 10:10.318
Of course.

10:14.363 --> 10:16.866
I think he's a bit feeble.

10:16.949 --> 10:18.367
Is that so?

10:19.660 --> 10:21.454
He's lost a lot of stamina.

10:26.876 --> 10:29.629
I mean, Jun-hui doesn't even catch
a cold that easily.

10:29.962 --> 10:31.213
I thought it was funny.

10:31.756 --> 10:33.215
What's so funny?

10:33.883 --> 10:36.469
Jun-hui, you work all night too often.

10:36.552 --> 10:37.970
That must be wearing you out.

10:38.429 --> 10:39.805
Everyone works as much as I do.

10:40.514 --> 10:42.683
Would you like me to prescribe him
some herbal medicine?

10:42.808 --> 10:44.894
Yes, please. Like you did for him--

10:44.977 --> 10:48.230
No, I'm good. I don't need it at all.

10:49.440 --> 10:50.691
- Gosh.
- No, thank you.

10:58.866 --> 11:02.578
Jun-hui, you should at least
eat more of this.

11:02.870 --> 11:04.664
Why don't you want herbal medicine?

11:04.747 --> 11:06.290
It's good for your stamina.

11:06.999 --> 11:09.502
I'm healthy. I'm not like Seung-ho.

11:10.503 --> 11:11.545
What's wrong with me?

11:12.505 --> 11:14.006
Don't you know?

11:14.590 --> 11:16.675
You always catch a cold in the winter.

11:16.842 --> 11:18.511
You're even weaker than your sister.

11:18.803 --> 11:20.471
That's because Jin-a is feisty.

11:21.430 --> 11:23.015
You shouldn't say that.

11:23.307 --> 11:25.476
It isn't good for a woman
to be called that.

11:26.435 --> 11:29.647
You two should find yourselves a woman

11:29.730 --> 11:31.399
who is quiet and good-tempered.

11:32.400 --> 11:34.318
You don't have to look too far.

11:35.027 --> 11:37.029
I'm talking about someone like
Jun-hui's late mother.

11:39.865 --> 11:41.283
Don't follow your dad's footsteps

11:41.909 --> 11:44.078
- and marry some--
- Mom.

11:45.246 --> 11:47.123
What? It's just between us.

11:49.458 --> 11:50.459
Jun-hui,

11:51.043 --> 11:52.962
I need you to marry someone nice,

11:53.045 --> 11:56.298
have children, and be happy.

11:56.382 --> 11:59.260
That way, I can happily reunite
with your mother in heaven.

11:59.343 --> 12:00.719
You understand what I mean, right?

12:02.596 --> 12:03.597
Of course.

12:12.356 --> 12:13.232
Gosh.

12:13.315 --> 12:14.608
What was that?

12:14.817 --> 12:16.610
Sorry. I was crossing my leg.

12:16.694 --> 12:17.695
Goodness.

12:18.612 --> 12:19.864
I'm sorry.

12:20.364 --> 12:21.740
- Eat up, Jun-hui.
- Okay.

12:22.992 --> 12:24.076
Don't do it.

12:48.726 --> 12:51.395
- I'm sorry, Dad.
- Drink it while it's hot.

12:51.896 --> 12:54.023
You must feel nauseous
since you cried so much.

12:55.441 --> 12:56.442
Okay.

13:00.988 --> 13:02.781
Do you want me to tell your mom?

13:04.450 --> 13:05.618
Can you tell her yourself?

13:07.495 --> 13:08.496
I have to.

13:12.833 --> 13:13.709
Is it okay...

13:14.585 --> 13:16.045
if I talk to Jun-hui?

13:19.548 --> 13:20.716
If you don't want me to...

13:24.094 --> 13:25.930
It's not that I don't want you to.

13:30.351 --> 13:31.477
What is it now?

13:33.521 --> 13:35.481
You can talk to him, but...

13:36.690 --> 13:38.651
That's fine, but...

13:39.610 --> 13:41.070
Please don't scold Jun-hui.

13:42.655 --> 13:43.656
Gosh.

13:46.158 --> 13:47.159
Okay?

13:47.743 --> 13:49.078
Do you like him that much?

13:52.998 --> 13:53.874
Yes.

14:05.761 --> 14:07.680
- Thank you.
- Goodbye.

14:14.228 --> 14:17.481
Jun-hui, come over to our house
with Gyeong-seon soon.

14:17.565 --> 14:18.649
- Okay?
- Okay.

14:18.732 --> 14:19.942
Okay, bye.

14:20.025 --> 14:21.694
- Okay, goodbye.
- Bye.

14:29.785 --> 14:32.329
- What?
- How unlike you to get nervous.

14:33.747 --> 14:36.333
No, you were nervous.
Why did you stop me from telling her?

14:37.001 --> 14:39.628
Hey, I already told Jin-a this.

14:39.712 --> 14:41.547
My mom will definitely faint
once she finds out.

14:43.007 --> 14:44.884
- You'll witness that soon.
- Soon?

14:46.594 --> 14:48.762
We can't keep it from her forever.
You'll help us, right?

14:49.346 --> 14:50.472
You're crazy.

14:50.931 --> 14:52.600
Don't even dream of it.

14:56.854 --> 14:59.106
- I'll see you. Bye.
- Bye.

15:11.744 --> 15:15.372
I brought home two servings.
Where did Jin-a go?

15:16.916 --> 15:19.877
- Where did she go?
- She had to meet someone.

15:19.960 --> 15:21.629
Who's she meeting on her day off?

15:21.712 --> 15:23.923
Someone might think she's dating someone.

15:24.715 --> 15:26.592
- Can I have some coke?
- Okay.

15:27.885 --> 15:30.596
I should step forward and take action.

15:30.846 --> 15:33.307
A friend of mine
wants to introduce Jin-a to a guy.

15:33.599 --> 15:34.725
- My gosh.
- Come on.

15:36.727 --> 15:39.271
My goodness. Eat up.

15:51.700 --> 15:52.743
Don't laugh.

15:52.826 --> 15:53.869
Okay.

15:58.958 --> 16:00.250
Are my eyes really that puffy?

16:00.751 --> 16:01.710
Yes.

16:03.295 --> 16:05.506
This is all because of you.

16:07.549 --> 16:08.926
You did well. I'm proud of you.

16:09.760 --> 16:11.345
Your eyes aren't that swollen.

16:11.428 --> 16:12.596
Forget it.

16:14.306 --> 16:16.308
Why did you cry?

16:18.769 --> 16:20.813
I tried not to cry.

16:22.231 --> 16:24.233
But I just couldn't help...

16:25.317 --> 16:26.860
I don't know.

16:28.862 --> 16:30.572
I wanted to be there with you.

16:30.990 --> 16:32.199
No, it's okay.

16:32.783 --> 16:35.285
I was able to have a talk with my dad.

16:35.744 --> 16:36.954
I'm glad I talked to him alone.

16:41.875 --> 16:42.918
I'll tell Gyeong-seon.

16:45.295 --> 16:47.172
I should be the one to tell her.

16:47.256 --> 16:48.924
It's Gyeong-seon of all people.

16:49.008 --> 16:50.300
Then what does that make me?

16:50.634 --> 16:52.594
It makes me seem like a coward.

16:52.678 --> 16:53.804
No, it doesn't.

16:53.887 --> 16:56.515
Let's not care about what others think.
What matters is how we think.

17:01.562 --> 17:03.897
- What?
- Were you always this confident?

17:04.815 --> 17:06.066
Are you falling for me again?

17:06.692 --> 17:08.360
I fell for you a long time ago.

17:10.237 --> 17:11.280
You did well.

17:12.823 --> 17:13.866
And thank you.

17:16.035 --> 17:17.619
All I did was cry.

18:59.680 --> 19:00.848
Hey, Gyeong-seon.

19:05.144 --> 19:06.145
Are you sleeping?

21:25.909 --> 21:29.830
I'M USING THE CAR

21:34.710 --> 21:36.295
Who's your boyfriend?

21:36.545 --> 21:39.881
Even Mr. Kong knows about him.
Why am I the only one who doesn't know?

21:40.507 --> 21:42.342
You're not the only one.

21:42.426 --> 21:45.595
And I didn't tell Mr. Kong the details.

21:46.263 --> 21:48.348
Does that mean
you're not going to tell me?

21:48.557 --> 21:49.641
Are you serious?

21:50.225 --> 21:51.643
Don't you have anything else to do?

21:52.394 --> 21:53.729
Ms. Seo canceled on me.

21:54.563 --> 21:57.065
Gyeong-seon did?
Is there a problem with the store?

21:57.566 --> 21:59.818
If that was the case,
she would've called me.

21:59.901 --> 22:02.321
I think it was regarding
something personal.

22:02.946 --> 22:05.157
Really? I wonder what's going on.

22:05.240 --> 22:07.492
She rarely cancels appointments.

22:08.076 --> 22:10.662
Stop changing the subject and tell me.

22:11.496 --> 22:14.416
Gosh, stop asking me.

22:14.541 --> 22:16.251
Your best friend is here.

22:16.918 --> 22:18.086
Se-yeong, you're here too.

22:18.795 --> 22:21.173
Why? You don't seem that glad to see me.

22:21.381 --> 22:23.091
We met at the office this morning.

22:23.175 --> 22:24.176
Why is she upset?

22:26.178 --> 22:28.430
You know who Jin-a's dating, don't you?

22:29.431 --> 22:31.183
Seriously, let's drop it.

22:31.308 --> 22:34.561
- Come on. Who is it?
- Can I get you something to drink?

22:35.395 --> 22:36.688
Seo Jun-hui.

22:38.690 --> 22:39.691
What?

22:46.615 --> 22:47.741
Hi.

22:59.169 --> 23:00.253
I know it's a bit random,

23:01.129 --> 23:02.672
but can I ask you something?

23:04.508 --> 23:07.344
You and Ms. Yoon are pretty close.

23:08.345 --> 23:10.555
Have you heard anything
about her boyfriend?

23:12.140 --> 23:14.434
- Why do you ask?
- You must have heard something.

23:15.310 --> 23:16.895
So she really does have a boyfriend.

23:18.355 --> 23:20.107
Do you know who she is dating
by any chance?

23:23.235 --> 23:24.319
Who is it?

23:26.488 --> 23:28.240
- It's me.
- You are what?

23:28.824 --> 23:29.699
Her boyfriend.

23:31.118 --> 23:32.160
Why?

23:32.494 --> 23:33.620
- What?
- What?

23:46.049 --> 23:47.467
You're being ridiculous.

23:48.260 --> 23:50.178
It's not like she stole
your boyfriend, is it?

23:50.762 --> 23:52.180
I never said she did!

23:52.264 --> 23:54.182
Then why are you all riled up?

23:54.516 --> 23:56.351
That's enough, okay?

23:57.394 --> 23:58.770
He flirted with me.

24:00.564 --> 24:01.606
When?

24:01.690 --> 24:04.151
- Then why did he go clubbing with me?
- We all went together.

24:04.234 --> 24:06.862
Does that mean he flirted
with me and Ye-eun too?

24:09.322 --> 24:10.323
Goodness.

24:14.202 --> 24:15.787
Anyway, you owe me an apology.

24:18.123 --> 24:19.499
She's being ridiculous. Gosh.

24:19.624 --> 24:21.334
Were you trying to upset her or what?

24:21.877 --> 24:24.004
- What did I do?
- Let me get through.

24:29.551 --> 24:30.594
Se-yeong.

24:33.054 --> 24:34.890
Don't apologize to me
if you don't mean it.

24:35.473 --> 24:37.225
If you want my apology,

24:37.434 --> 24:39.519
I'll apologize
for not telling you about it sooner.

24:41.563 --> 24:44.733
It's not because I'm prettier
or better than you in any sense,

24:44.858 --> 24:46.067
so don't be offended.

24:47.694 --> 24:49.112
I'm not that petty.

24:49.446 --> 24:51.489
Then please don't make it worse for me.

24:53.241 --> 24:54.951
Gyeong-seon doesn't know about it yet.

24:55.535 --> 24:56.870
I'm going to tell her soon,

24:57.037 --> 24:58.788
so pretend you know nothing
just until then.

25:02.667 --> 25:04.252
Do his parents know about it?

25:04.586 --> 25:06.796
I told you that their parents
are very picky.

25:08.256 --> 25:10.300
Thanks for your concern.

25:11.343 --> 25:13.094
Actually, his parents
aren't the only problem.

25:13.178 --> 25:14.888
Even his sister seems
to have high standards.

25:16.431 --> 25:18.141
Whatever. Good luck to you.

25:20.393 --> 25:21.311
Bye.

26:58.616 --> 27:01.619
Mom, I know you are already worried
that I might give your son a hard time.

27:04.372 --> 27:06.624
Why can't you consider
how I would feel for once?

27:06.708 --> 27:09.294
HERE LIES JEONG IN-HYE

27:09.377 --> 27:11.504
What are you going to do
if I give him a hard time?

27:15.467 --> 27:16.468
Mom.

27:24.434 --> 27:25.310
Mom.

27:27.645 --> 27:30.273
Don't make things hard for Jun-hui.

27:32.317 --> 27:33.985
I can't see him suffer.

28:14.651 --> 28:17.320
3 MISSED CALLS FROM JUN-HUI

28:26.996 --> 28:29.249
- What?
- Why didn't you answer earlier?

28:29.874 --> 28:30.959
Where are you now?

28:31.668 --> 28:33.086
At the store. Where else would I be?

28:47.934 --> 28:48.935
Yes.

28:49.853 --> 28:51.438
Of course I'm at work.

28:53.440 --> 28:54.441
Yes.

28:56.651 --> 28:57.652
Yes.

28:58.987 --> 29:00.739
I'm at the store.

29:02.907 --> 29:03.742
Right.

29:04.868 --> 29:06.494
Let's talk later.

29:38.109 --> 29:40.653
I was just thinking
that you look even prettier these days.

29:41.571 --> 29:43.072
Is it because you have a boyfriend now?

29:45.074 --> 29:46.075
Here you go.

29:59.881 --> 30:00.965
You know,

30:02.008 --> 30:04.594
I heard that there have been...

30:05.011 --> 30:06.012
How should I put this?

30:06.596 --> 30:08.640
I heard there have been
some misunderstanding.

30:11.935 --> 30:14.479
You see, he did that
because he cares about you a lot.

30:14.771 --> 30:15.897
He had no other intentions.

30:17.023 --> 30:20.485
Even I, myself, consider you
my own sister, and...

30:21.653 --> 30:22.779
How should I say it?

30:23.863 --> 30:24.864
Right, I care for you.

30:25.573 --> 30:27.784
I try to look out for you at times.

30:30.829 --> 30:33.998
I never thought that you'd feel that way
about me.

30:35.166 --> 30:36.918
I just wanted you to know that.

30:38.628 --> 30:42.507
I've always been nothing but nice to you,
Ms. Yoon.

30:46.678 --> 30:47.679
I see.

30:50.640 --> 30:52.016
- Mr. Nam.
- Yes.

30:53.059 --> 30:55.562
Do you have time tonight?

31:41.274 --> 31:42.567
Yes, come in.

31:47.155 --> 31:48.615
It's nothing important.

31:49.198 --> 31:50.992
Take female employees out
for dinner with that.

31:52.911 --> 31:55.830
You don't have all the survey responses.
I'll talk to them afterward.

31:56.789 --> 31:58.333
You can ask them verbally, sir.

31:58.833 --> 32:01.628
They don't even want to answer the survey.
They obviously won't tell me.

32:02.587 --> 32:03.588
Buy them something good.

32:04.839 --> 32:06.883
Let me know if you end up spending more.

32:27.111 --> 32:28.863
This is Jeong Yeong-in
from Marketing Team.

32:28.947 --> 32:30.156
Is the security manager there?

32:33.618 --> 32:34.994
It's me, Jeong Yeong-in.

32:35.078 --> 32:36.996
EMERGENCY OPERATIONS CENTER

32:52.553 --> 32:53.680
This is Jeong Yeong-in.

32:53.972 --> 32:55.848
Is Mr. Choi still in the office?

33:10.905 --> 33:13.116
There were no bad intentions
behind what I did.

33:13.199 --> 33:14.993
I just wanted to figure out the situation.

33:15.368 --> 33:17.161
That's... That's really all it was.

33:17.787 --> 33:20.331
- What situation?
- Well, I heard

33:20.581 --> 33:23.251
that a lot of our female employees
are very angry

33:23.334 --> 33:26.087
about sexual harassment occurring at work.

33:26.629 --> 33:28.047
So I wanted to check if it was true.

33:30.883 --> 33:32.051
I'll let you off the hook

33:33.302 --> 33:34.637
on one condition.

33:37.015 --> 33:38.683
Bring me evidence.

33:39.392 --> 33:42.353
Text messages, chat records,
social media posts,

33:42.979 --> 33:43.980
or even voice recordings.

33:44.647 --> 33:46.649
Bring me anything
that contains inappropriate remarks

33:46.733 --> 33:48.818
our male employees made
about the female employees.

34:02.999 --> 34:05.168
A movie theater that's more comfortable
than your house.

34:05.918 --> 34:08.713
Our theater is the first in the province
to adopt the latest technology

34:08.796 --> 34:11.674
to get rid of toxic substances
and fine dust.

34:11.799 --> 34:14.385
You will feel comfortable in your seats
throughout the entire movie.

34:14.469 --> 34:17.096
The spacious seats will enable you
to feel relaxed.

34:18.973 --> 34:23.227
The seats are also at the right height,
so nothing will hinder your view.

34:23.978 --> 34:25.938
We will soon premiere your dream.

34:28.816 --> 34:31.319
Please follow this instruction
during an emergency.

34:31.778 --> 34:33.863
For your safety,

34:33.946 --> 34:36.199
please take note of
our theater's location and exits

34:36.282 --> 34:39.911
including the nearest emergency exists.

34:43.039 --> 34:45.208
The following arrows indicate
the escape routes.

34:45.291 --> 34:47.668
Please follow our staff and escape safely

34:47.752 --> 34:49.754
in case of emergency.

35:22.703 --> 35:24.205
You're home already?

35:24.914 --> 35:28.126
I was outside for a while,
but I came home straight away.

35:30.795 --> 35:32.255
Is something wrong?

35:35.800 --> 35:37.051
Should I not ask?

35:39.178 --> 35:40.930
I think Gyeong-seon knows about us.

35:53.860 --> 35:55.862
No, I should be the one telling her.

35:56.154 --> 35:57.446
She has to hear it from me.

35:58.823 --> 36:00.158
I'll talk to you later.

36:19.218 --> 36:22.138
MY OTHER HALF, GYEONG-SEON

36:30.855 --> 36:32.773
CALLING MY OTHER HALF, GYEONG-SEON

38:08.452 --> 38:10.454
- Gyeong-seon.
- Not now.

38:46.824 --> 38:50.036
Before you tell me anything,
let me ask you this first.

38:52.580 --> 38:54.290
Do you two like each other?

38:57.126 --> 38:58.127
Or...

38:59.295 --> 39:01.339
are you just playing my brother?

39:06.886 --> 39:08.971
I like him more than he likes me.

39:52.515 --> 39:56.727
I know I can't make any excuses
for this situation.

39:58.187 --> 40:00.106
I also know

40:00.731 --> 40:04.944
that nothing I say will be able to
make you understand the whole situation.

40:06.487 --> 40:09.323
But let me tell you this, Gyeong-seon.

40:11.617 --> 40:13.661
I can't live without you.

40:15.538 --> 40:16.914
I know I have no right to say this.

40:17.748 --> 40:19.291
But that's just the truth.

40:21.377 --> 40:23.712
I can't live without you. I need you.

40:28.300 --> 40:29.385
What about Jun-hui?

40:32.638 --> 40:34.640
Don't you think you are being greedy?

40:35.766 --> 40:37.435
How can you be so selfish
and not care about

40:37.518 --> 40:39.437
how this can ruin my relationship
with my brother?

40:41.272 --> 40:42.857
I never took it that lightly.

40:43.482 --> 40:45.359
Then what were you thinking?

40:45.776 --> 40:48.112
How could you let things come this far?

40:53.451 --> 40:57.455
I'm sorry that I wasn't honest with you
from the beginning.

40:59.165 --> 41:00.291
Do you think

41:01.000 --> 41:03.669
I would've been happy for you two
if you had told me from the start?

41:06.839 --> 41:10.426
Do you really think this makes
any sense at all?

41:11.260 --> 41:13.387
Do you think what you're doing is right?

41:23.105 --> 41:24.106
Do you think...

41:24.940 --> 41:27.193
I'm being shameless?

41:27.860 --> 41:28.694
What?

41:31.489 --> 41:35.951
There's not a single thing
you don't know about me.

41:37.411 --> 41:39.455
We grew up together.

41:40.206 --> 41:42.500
So you know about my past relationships.

41:44.418 --> 41:46.504
And you even know

41:46.879 --> 41:48.547
my biggest secrets.

41:51.509 --> 41:53.552
I'm sure all those things bother you.

41:54.803 --> 41:55.679
Hey.

42:04.480 --> 42:06.440
What do you take me for?

42:07.858 --> 42:10.402
Are you seriously thinking

42:10.528 --> 42:13.197
that I would judge you based on your past?

42:14.573 --> 42:16.242
That's how frustrated I am.

42:18.786 --> 42:20.371
You can't even imagine

42:20.538 --> 42:23.165
how frustrated I am
with the whole situation.

42:24.333 --> 42:27.419
I don't even know how I managed to live
the past couple of days.

42:27.545 --> 42:30.673
That's how shocked I was. I felt betrayed.

42:31.340 --> 42:33.634
How could you, of all people...

42:38.806 --> 42:41.684
Then what am I supposed to do now?

42:43.269 --> 42:44.895
What do you want me to do?

42:46.564 --> 42:48.607
Do you want me to break up with him

42:49.733 --> 42:52.611
and wait until you're not angry
with me anymore?

42:53.445 --> 42:55.864
And if you can't forgive me
no matter what,

42:56.865 --> 42:58.867
should I just accept that

42:59.201 --> 43:02.288
and walk out of your life?

43:07.918 --> 43:09.545
Lay off the sarcasm, will you?

43:10.754 --> 43:12.590
I want to blame you if you would let me.

43:14.633 --> 43:16.468
What did I do wrong?

43:17.219 --> 43:18.512
There's nothing wrong

43:19.513 --> 43:21.015
with loving someone, don't you think?

43:25.603 --> 43:26.729
You won't like to hear this,

43:27.521 --> 43:28.897
but the fact that he's your brother

43:29.857 --> 43:31.609
never made me hesitate.

43:32.526 --> 43:33.861
Honestly,

43:36.864 --> 43:38.866
I couldn't afford to think
about how you would feel.

43:40.826 --> 43:42.494
That's how things came this far.

43:44.830 --> 43:45.956
I only thought about Jun-hui.

43:47.583 --> 43:49.418
I did not take anyone else
into consideration.

43:52.671 --> 43:54.673
That's how we ended up like this.

44:20.658 --> 44:21.700
What?

44:22.618 --> 44:23.661
Gyeong-seon.

44:24.953 --> 44:26.372
Don't hang up. Listen to me.

44:27.956 --> 44:30.501
I know you feel disappointed and betrayed.

44:32.044 --> 44:33.796
I do know

44:34.797 --> 44:37.216
that, I, of all people,
should not have done this to you.

44:39.510 --> 44:40.511
But Gyeong-seon,

44:42.471 --> 44:44.139
I couldn't give up on Jin-a.

44:46.433 --> 44:47.518
I started it.

44:48.644 --> 44:50.396
I started the whole thing by liking her.

44:53.023 --> 44:54.316
I like her so much.

44:56.443 --> 44:58.445
I wanted her by my side,
so I went out of my way.

45:02.574 --> 45:03.700
I'm sorry, Gyeong-seon.

45:06.286 --> 45:07.454
I'm really sorry, but...

45:10.999 --> 45:12.042
Just this once.

45:14.336 --> 45:15.754
Please understand me just this once.

45:18.340 --> 45:19.508
I'll take all the blame.

45:21.718 --> 45:24.388
I'll let you take it out on me
until you feel better.

45:25.389 --> 45:26.390
So please...

45:29.017 --> 45:30.936
Don't give Jin-a a hard time.

45:33.063 --> 45:34.064
You...

45:34.940 --> 45:36.400
Please, Gyeong-seon.

45:42.614 --> 45:43.657
You must be crazy.

47:12.996 --> 47:13.830
Okay.

47:17.709 --> 47:19.878
Jin-a's sleeping over
at Gyeong-seon's house.

47:21.004 --> 47:22.047
At Gyeong-seon's house?

47:22.130 --> 47:24.508
Goodness, you startled me.
What's the big deal?

47:25.175 --> 47:26.468
Well...

47:27.469 --> 47:29.638
She has to go to work tomorrow,
that's why.

47:29.721 --> 47:32.599
What are you talking about?
Tomorrow is weekend.

47:32.683 --> 47:33.559
Oh, right.

47:34.685 --> 47:36.019
Is she with Gyeong-seon?

47:36.436 --> 47:37.646
Of course.

47:38.021 --> 47:40.190
She called me using Gyeong-seon's phone.

47:41.066 --> 47:43.694
But why do you care so much
about Jin-a these days?

47:43.777 --> 47:46.113
- Gosh, I'm tired.
- Seriously?

47:46.196 --> 47:47.072
Let's go to sleep.

47:48.198 --> 47:49.491
Turn the lights off.

47:57.958 --> 48:00.168
Ouch. Hey!

48:00.961 --> 48:03.505
- Sorry.
- For goodness' sake.

48:26.028 --> 48:28.655
I'll call the police if you ring
the bell one more time.

48:28.822 --> 48:29.823
Hey--

48:41.918 --> 48:42.919
Gyeong-seon.

48:43.962 --> 48:45.172
Open the door.

48:50.636 --> 48:51.678
Hello?

49:09.071 --> 49:11.239
I was prettier back then.

49:11.823 --> 49:13.617
Excuse me? Are you serious?

49:13.784 --> 49:14.951
Look at me in this picture.

49:15.118 --> 49:17.454
My face is glowing. I look so beautiful.

49:17.788 --> 49:20.624
I shall beat you
until you come to your senses!

49:21.124 --> 49:22.709
Go ahead and kill me!

49:24.044 --> 49:26.838
- My gosh.
- Look at this.

49:27.756 --> 49:29.591
Time flies.

49:34.554 --> 49:37.015
This is when Jun-hui was a baby.

49:38.767 --> 49:41.520
He was so handsome even as a baby.

49:42.729 --> 49:44.272
Have some shame, will you?

49:45.232 --> 49:47.609
You'll have to put up with me
being like this from now on.

49:47.818 --> 49:49.277
Gosh.

49:50.821 --> 49:55.325
- You said you are okay with us dating.
- When did I say that? I said I'll try.

49:56.535 --> 49:58.161
- Come on.
- Please approve of us dating.

49:58.245 --> 50:00.163
Is this how you treat your sister-in-law?

50:01.707 --> 50:03.875
Let me teach you a lesson.

50:04.084 --> 50:05.252
- I'm sorry.
- Come on.

50:08.630 --> 50:10.173
Gosh.

50:12.676 --> 50:14.803
You'd better be good to me.

52:01.785 --> 52:03.745
- Who was that?
- Oh, my gosh.

52:06.289 --> 52:07.290
Who were they?

52:48.540 --> 52:49.875
Thank you, Gyeong-seon.

52:51.710 --> 52:53.503
You are crazy.
You must be out of your mind.

52:53.587 --> 52:55.714
- What's wrong with you?
- What's wrong with me?

52:55.797 --> 52:57.799
- Do you have a death wish?
- Wait. Gosh.

52:58.216 --> 53:00.093
- Let's talk it out.
- You wish!

53:00.385 --> 53:03.096
- You never even listen to me, you punk.
- What? It hurts.

53:03.555 --> 53:05.557
- It really hurts. Okay, I got it.
- I'll smack you...

53:08.268 --> 53:10.103
I went to see Mom.

53:12.022 --> 53:12.939
Why did you go alone?

53:15.358 --> 53:18.528
I went there to bad-mouth you.
Why would I take you with me?

53:22.866 --> 53:26.578
What would she have decided to do
had she been alive?

53:27.871 --> 53:31.082
I thought about
what she would have said to you.

53:35.211 --> 53:37.547
It's so predictable.

53:38.465 --> 53:39.883
She would have been like,

53:40.425 --> 53:42.928
"My gosh. Congratulations, Jun-hui.

53:43.011 --> 53:46.890
I really like Jin-a."
She would've said that right away.

53:49.184 --> 53:51.061
They say that blood is thicker than water.

53:51.811 --> 53:54.898
I know that Jin-a and I are best friends,

53:55.023 --> 53:56.316
but I put you before anyone else.

53:57.359 --> 53:59.361
I don't want to see you suffer in any way.

54:01.154 --> 54:02.197
I'll do my best.

54:02.405 --> 54:04.157
That alone would not change anything.

54:05.200 --> 54:07.035
Jin-a's parents... Gosh.

54:07.535 --> 54:08.536
Especially her mom--

54:08.787 --> 54:11.748
I know.
I know what you're trying to tell me.

54:23.009 --> 54:24.427
I've decided to understand

54:25.220 --> 54:29.015
the two of you, but that doesn't mean
that I'll be okay with everything.

54:29.432 --> 54:33.144
If something is wrong, or if anything
bothers me, I'll be direct about it.

54:33.353 --> 54:36.564
If you don't even let me do that,
you shouldn't call yourself my brother.

54:36.648 --> 54:38.692
I will consider you a shameless jerk.

54:40.944 --> 54:42.070
I won't do that.

54:49.369 --> 54:51.454
It won't be as easy as you think.

55:03.174 --> 55:05.927
How do you study engineering
when you're not even good with computers?

55:06.094 --> 55:08.513
My computer is fine.
The game itself is the problem.

55:08.596 --> 55:10.181
Come over as soon as you can.

55:11.975 --> 55:13.476
I don't think that's a good idea.

55:13.601 --> 55:16.062
Gosh, what are you worried about?
It's so unlike you.

55:16.521 --> 55:18.440
My parents are not home.

55:20.525 --> 55:21.901
But Jin-a isn't home either.

55:21.985 --> 55:23.069
Gosh.

55:28.950 --> 55:30.160
Enough is enough, okay?

55:38.460 --> 55:39.461
Stop.

56:03.068 --> 56:04.360
I'm leaving now.

56:05.278 --> 56:07.489
Take your time.
You might trip and fall if you run.

56:07.572 --> 56:09.908
Why would I run? I'm walking right now.

56:09.991 --> 56:13.453
Yes, okay. See you in a bit. Bye!

57:33.158 --> 57:34.325
Don't mind me.

57:41.791 --> 57:43.460
Watch this and memorize everything.

57:44.127 --> 57:45.086
Why should I?

57:45.170 --> 57:46.796
You can fix it whenever it doesn't work.

57:47.464 --> 57:49.841
Then when do you actually use your brain?

57:50.592 --> 57:51.759
At the right times.

57:52.218 --> 57:54.721
I use my brain
only when it's absolutely necessary.

57:56.681 --> 57:58.016
Are you home, Seung-ho?

57:58.600 --> 57:59.601
Yes.

58:04.397 --> 58:08.026
My gosh. You're here too, Jun-hui.

58:08.109 --> 58:09.777
- Hello.
- Why are you back already?

58:10.111 --> 58:12.030
Oh, they wanted to go for another round,

58:12.113 --> 58:15.116
but I came home as I didn't want to put up
with your dad's drunken rampage.

58:16.493 --> 58:18.036
Have you guys eaten yet?

58:18.119 --> 58:19.287
Yes, I had instant noodles.

58:19.412 --> 58:22.499
Gosh, why?
You should have had a proper meal.

58:22.582 --> 58:24.292
Why didn't you heat up the soup and fish--

58:24.375 --> 58:25.668
Gosh, it's fine.

58:28.671 --> 58:30.173
This is actually great.

58:30.256 --> 58:32.759
Let me ask your opinion
before your dad gets home.

58:33.092 --> 58:35.845
Have a look at this guy
and tell me what you think.

58:37.138 --> 58:38.014
Here.

58:41.809 --> 58:42.810
Who's this guy?

58:43.811 --> 58:46.064
Oh, he's Jin-a's...

58:46.147 --> 58:47.774
I told you about it the other day.

58:47.857 --> 58:50.443
A friend of mine wants
to set Jin-a up with this guy.

58:50.527 --> 58:52.153
Look.
He went to Seoul National University.

58:52.237 --> 58:53.863
What do you think?

58:55.156 --> 58:56.199
You see,

58:57.784 --> 59:00.620
I heard that men are better at telling
who's a good guy and who's not.

59:00.703 --> 59:03.414
Jun-hui, what do you think?
Does he look like a good guy to you?

59:03.748 --> 59:05.458
- Well...
- Mom, please.

59:05.625 --> 59:07.126
I told you not to do these things.

59:07.919 --> 59:10.171
Do you think I want to do this?

59:10.463 --> 59:12.340
Do you want Jin-a to grow old all alone?

59:12.632 --> 59:15.134
You ignored me when I asked you
to look for a nice guy for her.

59:15.218 --> 59:16.469
Why are you nagging me now?

59:18.888 --> 59:20.765
Don't say anything about this
to Jin-a, okay?

59:41.077 --> 59:42.954
Hey, do you need something?

59:43.788 --> 59:44.998
- No.
- Are you hungry?

59:45.081 --> 59:46.791
I was going to bring you guys some fruits.

59:48.418 --> 59:49.419
Well...

59:51.713 --> 59:53.381
There's something I'd like to tell you.

59:53.506 --> 59:55.592
What is it?
You want to tell me something? Go ahead.

59:59.304 --> 01:00:00.763
I guess it's something important.

01:00:02.307 --> 01:00:03.308
Yes.

01:00:03.516 --> 01:00:05.268
Then shall we have a talk
in the living room?

01:00:14.527 --> 01:00:16.738
Jun-hui, come and have a seat here.

01:00:22.327 --> 01:00:25.997
My gosh. What's the matter?

01:00:26.581 --> 01:00:28.708
Seung-ho, why is Jun-hui being like this?

01:00:30.752 --> 01:00:31.794
Jun-hui.

01:00:33.296 --> 01:00:35.340
- Ms. Kim.
- Yes, go ahead.

01:00:37.634 --> 01:00:39.385
Well, I'm actually...

01:00:39.844 --> 01:00:41.262
Yes, you can tell me--

01:00:51.856 --> 01:00:53.191
What... What's going on?

01:00:53.691 --> 01:00:55.610
That's what I want to ask you guys.

01:00:55.693 --> 01:00:58.905
He said he had something to tell me
and got down on his knees like this.

01:00:59.489 --> 01:01:02.909
Gosh, Jun-hui.
Whatever it is, you can tell me.

01:01:02.992 --> 01:01:06.412
Why are you acting like
you've done something wrong?

01:01:12.460 --> 01:01:13.419
What's going on?

01:01:14.045 --> 01:01:15.588
You guys...

01:01:16.381 --> 01:01:18.007
Why the heck are you two being like this?

01:01:24.847 --> 01:01:25.932
Hang on.

01:01:28.643 --> 01:01:29.602
Gosh, no way.

01:01:32.605 --> 01:01:34.524
The two of you...

01:01:35.983 --> 01:01:38.027
It's not what I'm thinking, right?

01:01:38.736 --> 01:01:39.779
Right?

01:01:41.489 --> 01:01:42.990
- Mom.
- Yes.

01:01:44.242 --> 01:01:45.159
I'm sorry, Ms. Kim.

01:01:47.495 --> 01:01:49.997
My goodness, how am I supposed to...

01:01:50.081 --> 01:01:51.999
- Gosh, this is...
- Mom, are you okay?

01:01:52.166 --> 01:01:55.044
- I can't believe this.
- Mom, try to calm down, okay?

01:01:55.670 --> 01:01:56.671
What?

01:01:56.754 --> 01:02:00.049
Did you... Did you know?

01:02:01.509 --> 01:02:03.678
Well... Yes.

01:02:04.262 --> 01:02:05.596
My goodness!

01:02:37.712 --> 01:02:41.090
To me, Jun-hui is just a man I like.

01:02:42.884 --> 01:02:44.385
I just wanted to check up on you.

01:02:44.761 --> 01:02:45.595
Don't cry.

01:02:45.678 --> 01:02:49.640
Have you ever wondered
how Jun-hui and I are doing?

01:02:49.724 --> 01:02:51.476
Don't hang out with Jun-hui from now on.

01:02:51.559 --> 01:02:53.978
Your daughter's life depends on this.

01:02:55.062 --> 01:02:57.440
I know you are with me on this.

01:02:57.523 --> 01:02:58.483
Don't you agree?

01:02:58.566 --> 01:03:01.152
I want you to gather proof
that shows our female employees

01:03:01.235 --> 01:03:02.403
have been mistreated.

01:03:02.487 --> 01:03:04.781
Everyone will be screwed
if I open my mouth.

01:03:04.864 --> 01:03:06.157
You're smart.

01:03:06.240 --> 01:03:07.617
What's love?

01:03:09.535 --> 01:03:11.788
Tell me what love is.

01:03:11.871 --> 01:03:13.748
Then what is love?
Do you even know what it is?

01:03:13.873 --> 01:03:15.500
Goodness.
Why don't you tell me what it is?

01:03:16.083 --> 01:03:17.960
I can do anything for you, Jin-a.

01:03:19.629 --> 01:03:20.588
What do you want?

01:03:22.298 --> 01:03:23.341
I want you.

01:03:25.426 --> 01:03:26.636
All I want is you, Jun-hui.

01:03:27.970 --> 01:03:30.056
Subtitle translation by Kim Su-hyeon
